\pc \bd 48\bd*

\s Inatushinda kufahamu Mapendo
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Inatushinda kufahamu \bd*\bd Mapendo yake\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd Mungu\bd*\bd  kwetu, Mapendo haya yanapita mapendo yetu sisi watu. Alimutuma Bwana Yesu kutoka kwake\bd*\bd  Mbingu\bd*\bd ni Kututafuta, wenye zambi, tupate kusamehewa.\bd*
\pc \bdit Inatushinda kufahamu \bdit*\bdit Mapendo \bdit*\bdit haha makubwa, Lakini tunajua kweli yatabakia daima.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Hata miaka inapita, vizazi vinakombolana, Na hata watu wa dunia wanakataa kuamini, Mapendo ya \bd*\bd Mungu\bd*\bd  ni sawa, makubwa sana na nguvu, Tayari kuokoa wote wanaotubu makosa.\bd*
\pc \bdit Inatushinda kufahamu Mapendo haha makubwa, Lakini tunajua kweli yatabakia daima.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Ee \bd*\bd Mungu\bd*\bd  mwenye pendo kubwa, Unifundishe kukupenda, Nipende vile watu wote na pendo unaonipenda. Nataka sana, Bwana Yesu, \bd*\bd Mapendo \bd*\bd yako makubwa Yanisukume kukufuata, kukupendeza daima.\bd*
\pc \bdit Inatushinda kufahamu Mapendo haha makubwa, Lakini tunajua kweli yatabakia daima.\bdit*
